title: 2014 BMW M6 Gran Coupe: The Best M Money Can Buy? Ignition E
description:
On this episode of Ignition, Jonny Lieberman gets behind the wheel of the newest M to grace the BMW lineup, the 2014 M6 Gran Coupe. It's big, it's powerful and it's expensive but is it the ultimate M? Stay tuned to find out.

Ignition appears every Monday
